roma dish, cover and place Varoma into position. Steam <b>8 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Serve garnished with fresh coriander leaves and lime segments."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Fillets can be secured with a cocktail stick if necessary.","For a main course, serve with fragrant Thai rice."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","2 portions"]}